html: SDBAUX Multi Charger Cable,3 in 1 Retractable USB Charging Cable Fast Charge with Micro USB Type C Phone Charger Cable…
description: 🥇3 in 1 USB Cable: Retractable charging cable with Phone, Micro USB and Type C 3 connector ports, it can provide multi-function charging for all your smart phones. Its maximum current is 3A (total). Please use 5V/3A output USB wall charger/USB car charger/power supply and power adapter. 🥇Universal Compatibility: Multiple phone charging cable is compatible with Android, Appl, Phone 12 11 Pro XSMax Xr X 8 7 6 5 4 Plus 5s 5c SE SE2, Samsung Galaxy S10 S9 S8 S7 A40 A50 A70 A3 A5 (2017) J3 J5 J7,Huawei P40 P30 P20 P10 Mate20/ Xiaomi/ Honor/ Google Pixel/ Kindle / HTC/ Nokia/ Sony/ Oneplus/ Blackberry/ Motorola/ PS5 PS4 PS3 PS2/ Bluetooth speakers/headphones/ Power bank/ Smartwatch/ Xbox/ Tablet/ USB Fan/ Alexa/ Nintendo Switch/ Echo Dot and More Mobile Phones.
